                    ========================================
                       CGI::Session::Driver::redis
                    ========================================

CGI::Session::Driver::redis is CGI::Session driver for redis.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  CGI::Session
  Redis

